<p>Ok, let's finish up. It's ok if <code>funFact</code> is empty - so don't add anything there.
The same is true for <code>isPublished</code>: we <em>could</em> add a constraint to make sure this
is a boolean, but the sanity validation on the form already takes care of that.</p>
